"""Inherintence:

The process of inherit all the properties and methods from parent class to child class

                    <<< SYNTAX >>>

class parentclassname():

    methods / staements

class childclassname(parentclassname):

    methods / staements

create object and then can call methods from both child class and parent class

                    <<< SYNTAX >>>
class Parent():
   
     body of the parent class

class derivedclassname(parent):

    Body of the derived class

"""



